      `Why most CPAs and advisors don’t talk about Roth-funded business investing — and why you’ll wish you’d known sooner.  (The secrets are legal, but rarely taught.)`,
      `How one investor used their Roth IRA to become a 25% owner in a business they never touched — and retired with *6 figures of tax-free income. (This is passive income, upgraded.)`
